{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place egg yolks, eggs and honey into mixing bowl and mix <b>10 sec\/speed 5<b>."," <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Add almond milk, milk and vanilla and cook <b>10 min\/70°C\/speed 2<b>.","Add cornflour. Using a fine-mesh sieve, sift nutmeg and cinnamon into mixing bowl and cook <b>14 min\/70°C\/speed 2<b>, until slightly thickened. Blend <b>20 sec\/speed 4<b> or until frothy. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk<\/strong>.","Strain eggnog through fine-mesh sieve into serving glasses. Dust with extra nutmeg and cinnamon before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["2 egg yolks","2 eggs","2 tbsp honey","400 g unsweetened almond milk","400 g milk","1 tsp natural vanilla extract","1 tsp cornflour","¼ tsp ground nutmeg, plus extra to serve","½ tsp ground cinnamon, plus extra to serve"]}],"id":"r122800","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-5kuK33Lpi5Q\/XZXZ1rMEt1I\/AAAAAAAAgMw\/dyjNoOGvhS0Ael5f_I7bxz67uzPfOto7QCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_nljgR9fkV2qHtwU7.png","title":"Spiced almond eggnog","publishedAt":"2017-04-02T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"9.1 g","fat":"11.2 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"17.1 g","calories":"850 kJ \/ 202 kcal"},"usefulItems":"fine mesh sieve, 4 small serving glasses","hintsAndTricks":["If you’re making this eggnog for a special occasion, you can add 1-2 tbsp brandy or dark rum when adding spices.","<strong>Dairy-free eggnog:<\/strong> Replace the cow’s milk and use 800 g almond milk."],"basicInfo":["medium","5m","30m","4 portions"]}